  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this study is to test, in the primary care setting, the efficacy of an innovative
      intervention program for children aged 2-5 years with a BMI over the 85th percentile and one
      overweight parent (BMI &gt;27 kg/m2.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
